### Template MSSearch

```{r echo=FALSE}
# template_MSSearch ---------------------------

library(multiDoE)

set.seed(123)

facts <- list(1, 2, 3)
units <- list(3, 3, 3)
levels <- 3
etas <- list(1, 1)
criteria <- "D"
model <- "interaction"

msopt <- MSOpt(facts, units, levels, etas, criteria, model)
mssearch <- MSSearch(msopt, 1, "Restarts", 100)

mssearch
```
